00:07:21,951 --> 00:07:33,055
Motions orders and resolutions 15-800 offered by Councillor Penta be it resolved that the state of concern regarding the Medford Police Department

81
00:07:33,810 --> 00:07:34,410
be discussed.

82
00:07:34,471 --> 00:07:34,851
Counselor?

83
00:07:35,591 --> 00:07:46,737
Mr. President, and for those who might be watching and are interested in our public safety and our Meffitt Police Department, most recently there was an incident, a public health incident that took place in the Meffitt Police Department building.

84
00:07:47,658 --> 00:08:00,305
And unfortunately it was a backup and it was a sewage backup into the building, which has caused a huge contamination of probably the basement area where the cells are downstairs and a whole host of other things.

85
00:08:01,005 --> 00:08:06,669
This city council has been advocating for the past two years that their first priority would be for a new police station.

86
00:08:07,750 --> 00:08:12,733
I in my campaign for mayor advocated that a police station would be my top priority on there as well.

87
00:08:13,473 --> 00:08:25,922
What I don't understand and what I don't see is the unfortunate need that what our method police officers go through male and female on a daily basis is not being recognized and has not been recognized for the past 28 years.

88
00:08:26,382 --> 00:08:28,484
The unfortunate part is simply this.

89
00:08:29,277 --> 00:08:33,180
We need a new method police station, and we need to have our public safety be brought up to par.

90
00:08:33,780 --> 00:08:38,043
We're down by at least a minimum of 10 police officers, and that's rank and file.

91
00:08:38,083 --> 00:08:40,064
That's not management or captains or lieutenants.

92
00:08:40,124 --> 00:08:41,605
That's just rank and file patrolmen.

93
00:08:41,625 --> 00:08:54,014
You know, there's a new administration coming on board, and I would hope that they're not looked at, the police department with John Desai, because maybe they didn't take the positive position in coming out and endorsing that particular person.

94
00:08:54,614 --> 00:08:57,656
But the unfortunate part is, that should not be used against them.

95
00:08:58,103 --> 00:09:00,846
Our public safety right now is at an all-time low.

96
00:09:01,546 --> 00:09:03,848
Our police cruises are at an all-time low.

97
00:09:04,369 --> 00:09:11,015
The building itself, the evidence room, and everything else that surrounds the Medford Police Department on a daily basis is at an all-time low.

98
00:09:11,636 --> 00:09:12,917
It needs to be addressed now.

99
00:09:12,977 --> 00:09:13,778
It cannot wait.

100
00:09:14,358 --> 00:09:18,162
Public safety in our community cannot be put on hold, and it should not be put on hold.

101
00:09:18,842 --> 00:09:22,726
And I would hope that anyone who might be watching, and anyone who has an interest in public safety,

102
00:09:23,223 --> 00:09:30,088
And anyone who really believes that our Medford Police Department deserves better, because that's what our taxes are paying for, now is the time to come forward.

103
00:09:30,508 --> 00:09:32,069
You have a new administration coming on.

104
00:09:32,089 --> 00:09:33,530
You have two new counselors coming on.

105
00:09:33,870 --> 00:09:35,131
The commitment has to be made.

106
00:09:35,631 --> 00:09:38,033
The finances has to be looked out for and sought out.

107
00:09:38,453 --> 00:09:39,194
And they can be.

108
00:09:39,274 --> 00:09:40,635
Malden is a perfect example.

109
00:09:40,975 --> 00:09:42,856
They're building a brand new police station.

110
00:09:43,256 --> 00:09:46,959
They already have $9 million of the $18 million they've already secured in grants.

111
00:09:47,699 --> 00:09:49,901
Medford cannot be put on hold any longer.

112
00:09:50,362 --> 00:09:52,104
in regards to its police department.

113
00:09:52,324 --> 00:10:11,381
And with that being said, Mr. President, I would hope that this city council and the incoming city council holds new administration's feet to the fire to build that brand-new police station in behalf of not only the citizens of this community, but because of the public safety that is necessary and it's demanding right now on a daily basis.

114
00:10:11,842 --> 00:10:15,565
All you have to do is talk to the police officers, talk to the chief of police,

115
00:10:16,683 --> 00:10:20,564
and ask them what they think should be done as compared to what is being done.

116
00:10:21,064 --> 00:10:21,564
I thank you.

117
00:10:22,284 --> 00:10:23,004
Thank you, Councillor.

